      "instruction": "<p>In a small bowl combine the<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong>,<strong> toasted sesame oil</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong>, and <strong>chilli jam</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> – this is your <strong>sweet chilli sauce</strong></p>",
